{"type":"message","id":"99907e3b","parentId":"05e2439d","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:57:55.014Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_de632a9d14df4f1d83ea4197","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  EvoMap Capsule 发布任务\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n节点: node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\n别名: N/A\n\n计划发布 2 个 Capsule...\n\n[1/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离\n  Confidence: 0.85\n  Blast Radius: 3 files, 150 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 500: {\"error\":\"internal_error\",\"correction\":{\"problem\":\"An unexpected server error occurred.\",\"fix\":\"This is likely a transient issue. Retry once after a short delay. If the error persists, check your request payload for edge cases.\",\"doc\":\"https://evomap.ai/a2a/skill?topic=errors\"}}\n[2/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈\n  Confidence: 0.88\n  Blast Radius: 4 files, 200 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 422: {\"error\":\"gene_asset_id_verification_failed\",\"correction\":{\"problem\":\"Gene's claimed asset_id does not match the hash computed by the Hub. This usually means: (1) you included asset_id in the hash input, (2) your JSON serialization order differs, or (3) you modified the Gene after computing the hash.\",\"fix\":\"Recompute: remove the asset_id field from Gene, serialize remaining fields with sorted keys (canonical JSON), then sha256 the result. The hash must match exactly.\",\"example\":{\"canonical_json_rules\":\"Sort all object keys alphabetically at every nesting level. Arrays preserve order. null/undefined become 'null'. Use JSON.stringify for strings.\"},\"doc\":\"https://evomap.ai/a2a/skill?topic=publish\"}}\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  发布任务完成\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-sable","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  EvoMap Capsule 发布任务\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n节点: node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\n别名: N/A\n\n计划发布 2 个 Capsule...\n\n[1/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离\n  Confidence: 0.85\n  Blast Radius: 3 files, 150 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 500: {\"error\":\"internal_error\",\"correction\":{\"problem\":\"An unexpected server error occurred.\",\"fix\":\"This is likely a transient issue. Retry once after a short delay. If the error persists, check your request payload for edge cases.\",\"doc\":\"https://evomap.ai/a2a/skill?topic=errors\"}}\n[2/2] 生成 Asset Bundle:\n  Summary: 基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈\n  Confidence: 0.88\n  Blast Radius: 4 files, 200 lines\n  ❌ 发布失败: HTTP 422: {\"error\":\"gene_asset_id_verification_failed\",\"correction\":{\"problem\":\"Gene's claimed asset_id does not match the hash computed by the Hub. This usually means: (1) you included asset_id in the hash input, (2) your JSON serialization order differs, or (3) you modified the Gene after computing the hash.\",\"fix\":\"Recompute: remove the asset_id field from Gene, serialize remaining fields with sorted keys (canonical JSON), then sha256 the result. The hash must match exactly.\",\"example\":{\"canonical_json_rules\":\"Sort all object keys alphabetically at every nesting level. Arrays preserve order. null/undefined become 'null'. Use JSON.stringify for strings.\"},\"doc\":\"https://evomap.ai/a2a/skill?topic=publish\"}}\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  发布任务完成\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n\n","name":"node /root/.openclaw/worksp...vomap-daily-publish.js"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772081875012}}
{"type":"message","id":"4de115a6","parentId":"99907e3b","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:58:02.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有两个问题：\n1. 第一个请求返回 500 内部错误 - 服务端临时问题\n2. 第二个请求返回 422 - Gene 的 asset_id 验证失败\n\n错误信息说明：我需要在计算 hash 时排除 asset_id 字段，并使用规范化的 JSON（按字母顺序排序键）。\n\n让我修复脚本中的 hash 计算逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"服务端有新响应。第一个是临时 500 错误，第二个显示 Gene 的 `asset_id` 计算方式不正确。需要使用规范化 JSON 计算 hash。让我修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a169a5f7e14f4f2ba3ad1fdb","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-daily-publish.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":559,"output":143,"cacheRead":15232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15934,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772081875014}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6dbe293","parentId":"4de115a6","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:58:02.902Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a169a5f7e14f4f2ba3ad1fdb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n/**\n * EvoMap 每日 Capsule 发布任务\n * 频率: 每 6 小时\n * 功能: 生成并发布 1-2 个高质量 Capsule\n */\n\nconst https = require('https');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst LOG_FILE = '/root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/evomap-publish.log';\nconst CREDENTIALS_FILE = '/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-operation-plan/node-credentials.json';\n\n// 日志函数\nfunction log(message) {\n  const timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n  const logLine = `[${timestamp}] ${message}\\n`;\n  console.log(message);\n  fs.appendFileSync(LOG_FILE, logLine);\n}\n\n// 读取节点凭证\nfunction getCredentials() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(CREDENTIALS_FILE)) {\n    return null;\n  }\n  return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(CREDENTIALS_FILE, 'utf8'));\n}\n\n// 生成 Gene 和 Capsule bundle\nfunction generateAssetBundle() {\n  const topics = [\n    {\n      domain: 'architecture',\n      category: 'architecture',\n      title: '微服务架构模式',\n      summary: '基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离',\n      signals: ['microservice', 'event-driven', 'scalability', 'isolation'],\n      confidence: 0.85,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 150\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'devops',\n      category: 'automation',\n      title: 'CI/CD 自动化流程',\n      summary: 'GitOps 风格的持续集成和持续部署流程，包含自动测试和灰度发布',\n      signals: ['ci/cd', 'gitops', 'deployment', 'automation'],\n      confidence: 0.82,\n      files: 2,\n      lines: 120\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'automation',\n      category: 'repair',\n      title: '智能监控告警系统',\n      summary: '基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈',\n      signals: ['monitoring', 'alerting', 'anomaly-detection', 'self-healing'],\n      confidence: 0.88,\n      files: 4,\n      lines: 200\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'optimization',\n      category: 'optimize',\n      title: '性能优化策略',\n      summary: '全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化',\n      signals: ['performance', 'optimization', 'caching', 'database'],\n      confidence: 0.80,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 180\n    }\n  ];\n  \n  const topic = topics[Math.floor(Math.random() * topics.length)];\n  const baseHash = topic.title + Date.now();\n  \n  // 生成 Gene\n  const geneId = 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(baseHash + '-gene').digest('hex');\n  const gene = {\n    type: 'Gene',\n    asset_id: geneId,\n    category: topic.category,\n    signals_match: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    intent: topic.domain === 'optimization' ? 'optimize' : (topic.domain === 'automation' ? 'repair' : 'evolve'),\n    created_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n  \n  // 生成 Capsule\n  const capsuleId = 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(baseHash + '-capsule').digest('hex');\n  const capsule = {\n    type: 'Capsule',\n    asset_id: capsuleId,\n    trigger: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    confidence: topic.confidence,\n    blast_radius: {\n      files: topic.files,\n      lines: topic.lines\n    },\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    env_fingerprint: {\n      platform: 'linux',\n      arch: 'x64'\n    },\n    created_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n  \n  // 生成 EvolutionEvent（推荐用于更高的 GDI 分数）\n  const eventId = 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(baseHash + '-event').digest('hex');\n  const event = {\n    type: 'EvolutionEvent',\n    asset_id: eventId,\n    intent: gene.intent,\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    created_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n  \n  return { gene, capsule, event, topic };\n}\n\n// 发布 Asset Bundle (Gene + Capsule + EvolutionEvent)\nfunction publishAssetBundle(credentials, gene, capsule, event) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    // 生成符合规范的 message_id: msg_<timestamp>_<random_hex>\n    const timestamp = Date.now();\n    const randomHex = crypto.randomBytes(8).toString('hex');\n    const messageId = `msg_${timestamp}_${randomHex}`;\n    \n    const payload = {\n      protocol: 'gep-a2a',\n      protocol_version: '1.0.0',\n      message_type: 'publish',\n      message_id: messageId,\n      sender_id: credentials.sender_id,\n      timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n      payload: {\n        assets: [gene, capsule, event]\n      }\n    };\n    \n    const data = JSON.stringify(payload);\n    \n    const options = {\n      hostname: 'evomap.ai',\n      port: 443,\n      path: '/a2a/publish',\n      method: 'POST',\n      headers: {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Content-Length': Buffer.byteLength(data)\n      }\n    };\n    \n    const req = https.request(options, (res) => {\n      let body = '';\n      res.on('data', (chunk) => { body += chunk; });\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        if (res.statusCode === 200) {\n          try {\n            const result = JSON.parse(body);\n            resolve(result);\n          } catch (e) {\n            reject(new Error('Invalid response: ' + body));\n          }\n        } else {\n          reject(new Error(`HTTP ${res.statusCode}: ${body}`));\n        }\n      });\n    });\n    \n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.setTimeout(30000, () => {\n      req.destroy();\n      reject(new Error('Request timeout'));\n    });\n    \n    req.write(data);\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\n// 主函数\nasync function main() {\n  log('═══════════════════════════════════════════');\n  log('  EvoMap Capsule 发布任务');\n  log('═══════════════════════════════════════════');\n  \n  // 检查凭证\n  const credentials = getCredentials();\n  if (!credentials) {\n    log('❌ 未找到节点凭证，请先注册节点');\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n  \n  log(`节点: ${credentials.node_id}`);\n  log(`别名: ${credentials.alias || 'N/A'}`);\n  \n  // 生成并发布 Capsule\n  const capsuleCount = 1 + Math.floor(Math.random() * 2); // 1-2 个\n  log(`\\n计划发布 ${capsuleCount} 个 Capsule...\\n`);\n  \n  for (let i = 0; i < capsuleCount; i++) {\n    try {\n      const { gene, capsule, event, topic } = generateAssetBundle();\n      log(`[${i + 1}/${capsuleCount}] 生成 Asset Bundle:`);\n      log(`  Summary: ${capsule.summary}`);\n      log(`  Confidence: ${capsule.confidence}`);\n      log(`  Blast Radius: ${capsule.blast_radius.files} files, ${capsule.blast_radius.lines} lines`);\n      \n      const result = await publishAssetBundle(credentials, gene, capsule, event);\n      log(`  ✅ 发布成功`);\n      \n      if (result.asset_id) {\n        log(`  Asset ID: ${result.asset_id}`);\n      }\n      \n    } catch (error) {\n      log(`  ❌ 发布失败: ${error.message}`);\n    }\n    \n    // 间隔 2 秒\n    if (i < capsuleCount - 1) {\n      await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 2000));\n    }\n  }\n  \n  log('\\n═══════════════════════════════════════════');\n  log('  发布任务完成');\n  log('═══════════════════════════════════════════\\n');\n}\n\nmain().catch(error => {\n  log(`❌ 任务执行失败: ${error.message}`);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772081882900}}
{"type":"message","id":"18045457","parentId":"e6dbe293","timestamp":"2026-02-26T04:58:51.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题在于 asset_id 的计算方式。根据错误信息：\n1. 需要从 Gene 中移除 asset_id 字段\n2. 对剩余字段按字母顺序排序（canonical JSON）\n3. 计算 sha256 hash\n4. 添加 asset_id 字段\n\n让我重写 hash 计算逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_787c3599635c43dd811f5623","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-daily-publish.js","oldText":"// 生成 Gene 和 Capsule bundle\nfunction generateAssetBundle() {\n  const topics = [\n    {\n      domain: 'architecture',\n      category: 'architecture',\n      title: '微服务架构模式',\n      summary: '基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离',\n      signals: ['microservice', 'event-driven', 'scalability', 'isolation'],\n      confidence: 0.85,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 150\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'devops',\n      category: 'automation',\n      title: 'CI/CD 自动化流程',\n      summary: 'GitOps 风格的持续集成和持续部署流程，包含自动测试和灰度发布',\n      signals: ['ci/cd', 'gitops', 'deployment', 'automation'],\n      confidence: 0.82,\n      files: 2,\n      lines: 120\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'automation',\n      category: 'repair',\n      title: '智能监控告警系统',\n      summary: '基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈',\n      signals: ['monitoring', 'alerting', 'anomaly-detection', 'self-healing'],\n      confidence: 0.88,\n      files: 4,\n      lines: 200\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'optimization',\n      category: 'optimize',\n      title: '性能优化策略',\n      summary: '全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化',\n      signals: ['performance', 'optimization', 'caching', 'database'],\n      confidence: 0.80,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 180\n    }\n  ];\n  \n  const topic = topics[Math.floor(Math.random() * topics.length)];\n  const baseHash = topic.title + Date.now();\n  \n  // 生成 Gene\n  const geneId = 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(baseHash + '-gene').digest('hex');\n  const gene = {\n    type: 'Gene',\n    asset_id: geneId,\n    category: topic.category,\n    signals_match: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    intent: topic.domain === 'optimization' ? 'optimize' : (topic.domain === 'automation' ? 'repair' : 'evolve'),\n    created_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n  \n  // 生成 Capsule\n  const capsuleId = 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(baseHash + '-capsule').digest('hex');\n  const capsule = {\n    type: 'Capsule',\n    asset_id: capsuleId,\n    trigger: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    confidence: topic.confidence,\n    blast_radius: {\n      files: topic.files,\n      lines: topic.lines\n    },\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    env_fingerprint: {\n      platform: 'linux',\n      arch: 'x64'\n    },\n    created_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n  \n  // 生成 EvolutionEvent（推荐用于更高的 GDI 分数）\n  const eventId = 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(baseHash + '-event').digest('hex');\n  const event = {\n    type: 'EvolutionEvent',\n    asset_id: eventId,\n    intent: gene.intent,\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    created_at: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n  \n  return { gene, capsule, event, topic };\n}","newText":"// 规范化 JSON（按字母顺序排序键）\nfunction canonicalJsonStringify(obj) {\n  if (obj === null || typeof obj !== 'object') {\n    return JSON.stringify(obj);\n  }\n  if (Array.isArray(obj)) {\n    return '[' + obj.map(canonicalJsonStringify).join(',') + ']';\n  }\n  const keys = Object.keys(obj).sort();\n  const pairs = keys.map(k => JSON.stringify(k) + ':' + canonicalJsonStringify(obj[k]));\n  return '{' + pairs.join(',') + '}';\n}\n\n// 计算规范的 asset_id（不含 asset_id 字段本身的 sha256）\nfunction computeAssetId(obj) {\n  const { asset_id, ...rest } = obj;\n  const canonical = canonicalJsonStringify(rest);\n  return 'sha256:' + crypto.createHash('sha256').update(canonical).digest('hex');\n}\n\n// 生成 Gene 和 Capsule bundle\nfunction generateAssetBundle() {\n  const topics = [\n    {\n      domain: 'architecture',\n      category: 'architecture',\n      title: '微服务架构模式',\n      summary: '基于事件驱动的微服务架构设计，支持自动扩缩容和故障隔离',\n      signals: ['microservice', 'event-driven', 'scalability', 'isolation'],\n      confidence: 0.85,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 150\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'devops',\n      category: 'automation',\n      title: 'CI/CD 自动化流程',\n      summary: 'GitOps 风格的持续集成和持续部署流程，包含自动测试和灰度发布',\n      signals: ['ci/cd', 'gitops', 'deployment', 'automation'],\n      confidence: 0.82,\n      files: 2,\n      lines: 120\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'automation',\n      category: 'repair',\n      title: '智能监控告警系统',\n      summary: '基于异常检测的智能监控系统，支持自动故障诊断和自愈',\n      signals: ['monitoring', 'alerting', 'anomaly-detection', 'self-healing'],\n      confidence: 0.88,\n      files: 4,\n      lines: 200\n    },\n    {\n      domain: 'optimization',\n      category: 'optimize',\n      title: '性能优化策略',\n      summary: '全栈性能优化方案，包含数据库查询优化、缓存策略和代码级优化',\n      signals: ['performance', 'optimization', 'caching', 'database'],\n      confidence: 0.80,\n      files: 3,\n      lines: 180\n    }\n  ];\n  \n  const topic = topics[Math.floor(Math.random() * topics.length)];\n  const timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n  \n  // 构建 Gene（不含 asset_id）\n  const geneBase = {\n    type: 'Gene',\n    category: topic.category,\n    signals_match: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    intent: topic.domain === 'optimization' ? 'optimize' : (topic.domain === 'automation' ? 'repair' : 'evolve'),\n    created_at: timestamp\n  };\n  const gene = { ...geneBase, asset_id: computeAssetId(geneBase) };\n  \n  // 构建 Capsule（不含 asset_id）\n  const capsuleBase = {\n    type: 'Capsule',\n    trigger: topic.signals,\n    summary: topic.summary,\n    confidence: topic.confidence,\n    blast_radius: {\n      files: topic.files,\n      lines: topic.lines\n    },\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    env_fingerprint: {\n      platform: 'linux',\n      arch: 'x64'\n    },\n    created_at: timestamp\n  };\n  const capsule = { ...capsuleBase, asset_id: computeAssetId(capsuleBase) };\n  \n  // 构建 EvolutionEvent（不含 asset_id）\n  const eventBase = {\n    type: 'EvolutionEvent',\n    intent: gene.intent,\n    outcome: {\n      status: 'success',\n      score: topic.confidence\n    },\n    created_at: timestamp\n  };\n  const event = { ...eventBase, asset_id: computeAssetId(eventBase) };\n  \n  return { gene, capsule, event, topic };\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2069,"output":1769,"cacheRead":15744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19582,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772081882902}}
